        } else {
            iframe.style.width = '60%';
        }
    });
});
```

This JavaScript code adjusts the iframe's width based on the viewport width and also listens for window resize events to adjust the width dynamically. However, for most use cases, the CSS media queries approach is more efficient and recommended.

