This command will prompt the user to enter some input and then save that input to a file named `input.txt`. Note that this approach is more of a workaround and not the standard way to handle user input in Terraform.

For most use cases, Terraform provides a more straightforward method to ask for user input using `variable` blocks:

```hcl
variable "user_input" {
