- **Performance**: Dynamically loading iframe sources can impact page load times. Optimize your implementation to minimize performance impacts.

These examples provide a basic framework for implementing iframes server-side in Next.js 13. Depending on your specific requirements, you might need to adjust the approach, especially concerning data fetching and security considerations.

